    "steam_appid": 3333990,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333990/extras/0016a1c42c21ee7dc014ae31f1b231b0.avif?t=1755529072\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333990/extras_big/0016a1c42c21ee7dc014ae31f1b231b0.avif?t=1755529072 width=800 height=339 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>COVENANT</strong> is a <strong><i>FIRST-PERSON DARK-FANTASY ACTION ADVENTURE GAME </i></strong>where you'll wilder a large interconnected world, passing through kingdoms and peril - discovering fighting stances, spells, weapons, and gear forged by the men of renown, heroes of old.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333990/extras/f7423ab36bd484f1a41d5451d03dd3d2.avif?t=1755529072\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333990/extras_big/f7423ab36bd484f1a41d5451d03dd3d2.avif?t=1755529072 width=800 height=109 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Seek the Old Notes.</strong><i></i><br><i>Experience Creation through the eyes of the last living messenger. The oldest of your kind, Malach, has fallen to the abyss - leaving in his wake a trail of destruction. You must follow in the footsteps of his final days in order to uncover the nature of his fall - and in doing so, reveal the slumbering forces hidden within Creation.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333990/extras/f36ec78060bf1c55e53453cab54e512f.poster.avif?t=1755529072\" width=800 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333990/extras/f36ec78060bf1c55e53453cab54e512f.webm?t=1755529072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333990/extras/f36ec78060bf1c55e53453cab54e512f.mp4?t=1755529072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore an Interconnected  world -</strong> Creation is a sprawling and interconnected land of myth. Exploration is part of the journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333990/extras/fd11770f616989f88032e027214274ef.poster.avif?t=1755529072\" width=800 height=364 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333990/extras/fd11770f616989f88032e027214274ef.webm?t=1755529072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333990/extras/fd11770f616989f88032e027214274ef.mp4?t=1755529072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Bosses </i></strong>- Creatures of fallen empires and heroes long lost stand in your way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333990/extras/d8b540426cd4eec8f0f37008c9376611.poster.avif?t=1755529072\" width=800 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333990/extras/d8b540426cd4eec8f0f37008c9376611.webm?t=1755529072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333990/extras/d8b540426cd4eec8f0f37008c9376611.mp4?t=1755529072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Master close quarter combat like never before (in first-person!)</strong></i> - Kick, grab, roll, and execute anyone who stands in your way. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Expressive and powerful movement abilities </strong></i>- Skillfully pivot your slide around corners, down slopes, kick or jump off walls, and alternate between rolling or side-stepping in intimate duels. These are easy to use but will take time to master.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333990/extras/08bb5db83c0f9434220e0998caf523ce.poster.avif?t=1755529072\" width=800 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333990/extras/08bb5db83c0f9434220e0998caf523ce.webm?t=1755529072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333990/extras/08bb5db83c0f9434220e0998caf523ce.mp4?t=1755529072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333990/extras/6ceafc7545b23349606ab971b0656a1b.poster.avif?t=1755529072\" width=800 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333990/extras/6ceafc7545b23349606ab971b0656a1b.webm?t=1755529072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333990/extras/6ceafc7545b23349606ab971b0656a1b.mp4?t=1755529072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333990/extras/7fd02018a97755bcd38b212ed709fa02.poster.avif?t=1755529072\" width=800 height=364 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333990/extras/7fd02018a97755bcd38b212ed709fa02.webm?t=1755529072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333990/extras/7fd02018a97755bcd38b212ed709fa02.mp4?t=1755529072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333990/extras/b96ce03f9c44eb3c671243b5bb3af700.avif?t=1755529072\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333990/extras_big/b96ce03f9c44eb3c671243b5bb3af700.avif?t=1755529072 width=800 height=109 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333990/extras/6a89ffa751cbb7b2c4a8c3fec0bb7b14.poster.avif?t=1755529072\" width=800 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333990/extras/6a89ffa751cbb7b2c4a8c3fec0bb7b14.webm?t=1755529072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333990/extras/6a89ffa751cbb7b2c4a8c3fec0bb7b14.mp4?t=1755529072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stances don't just change your elemental affinity - </strong><strong><i>they change your entire fighting style</i></strong><i> down to the way you run, jump, kick, and slide</i>. Each stance's play style varies drastically - and every may take a lifetime to master.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333990/extras/71810866c32fdbca25d27eb195c703b4.poster.avif?t=1755529072\" width=750 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333990/extras/71810866c32fdbca25d27eb195c703b4.webm?t=1755529072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333990/extras/71810866c32fdbca25d27eb195c703b4.mp4?t=1755529072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Powerful build-crafting opportunities</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333990/extras/1697d113839ee94da82836821595d968.webp?t=1755529072\" width=32 height=32 /></span>   <strong><i>JOIN OUR COMMUNITY DISCORD</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333990/extras/e7b445c1ebec7f67b66c5a0ff55a0959.avif?t=1755529072\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333990/extras_big/e7b445c1ebec7f67b66c5a0ff55a0959.avif?t=1755529072 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Greater Things Are Coming</i></p>",
